137
00:07:58,545 --> 00:08:01,481
What's more, they even go so far as to destroy evidence.

138
00:08:01,548 --> 00:08:05,419
(Manami) So, does that mean Ai-chan is separate?

139
00:08:05,485 --> 00:08:08,922
>> I was the first to enter the warehouse and made it my hideout.

140
00:08:08,989 --> 00:08:11,425
Even before you all came.

141
00:08:11,491 --> 00:08:14,494
