181
00:10:34,568 --> 00:10:38,505
And it's not dawn anymore →

182
00:10:38,572 --> 00:10:42,509
I was wondering if they would kill each other if I set it within an hour.→

183
00:10:42,576 --> 00:10:45,012
I thought... this is it.

184
00:10:45,078 --> 00:10:48,515
(Kuroiwa) He simply said, ``That's strange.''

185
00:10:48,582 --> 00:10:52,519
>> Yes! It's probably funny.

186
00:10:52,586 --> 00:10:55,022
People like me →

187
