201
00:11:52,646 --> 00:11:54,147
>> [Wow! ]

202
00:11:57,651 --> 00:12:01,088
(Manami's voice) Because I couldn't respond to your feelings...

203
00:12:01,154 --> 00:12:09,596
>> [Sound of keyboard hitting]

204
00:12:10,664 --> 00:12:13,667
(Manami's voice) Just a sticky resentment.

205
00:12:17,170 --> 00:12:20,107
(Manami) Um... When I go to prison... →

206
00:12:20,173 --> 00:12:23,110
He calls himself a psychopath and is like a death game →

207
00:12:23,176 --> 00:12:25,112
It's better to stop.

208
00:12:25,178 --> 00:12:27,114
It's probably too painful for me to pull out.

209
00:12:27,180 --> 00:12:31,118
