234
00:14:07,147 --> 00:14:10,650
As long as I'm alive...

235
00:14:12,152 --> 00:14:14,154
(Manami) Kuroiwa-kun is right.

236
00:14:15,655 --> 00:14:18,091
It won't last forever.

237
00:14:18,158 --> 00:14:20,660
To love you

238
00:14:23,663 --> 00:14:29,102
(Manami) You hurt the people I care about too much.

239
00:14:29,169 --> 00:14:33,106
Illness and painful past →

240
00:14:33,173 --> 00:14:36,042
Face your sins seriously →

241
00:14:36,109 --> 00:14:39,546
The lives they have tried to build →

242
00:14:39,613 --> 00:14:42,048
You stole it.

243
00:14:42,115 --> 00:14:46,052
You who ran away from facing →

244
00:14:46,119 --> 00:14:49,055
I'll never be able to match them.

245
